reviewText: We bought this for my mom for Christmas and she is really happy with it. She has experience with Tai Chi and was really happy to learn more about Qi Gong from Lee Holden.
Lee Holden's routines on video or DVD are marvelous exercise  and meditation practices.
My favorite of his videos. It really will increase your energy levels.
Tape came in excellent condition and I was able to view and use it-as is-with no issues. Came very timely,too. Thank you
